编写递归算法,将二叉树中所有结点的左、右子树相互交换。Status ExchangeBiTree(BiTree& T){ BiTree p; if(T){ p=T->lchild; T->lchild=T->rchild; T->rchild=p; ExchangeBiTree(T->lchild); ____ } return OK;}
A. ExchangeBiTree(p);
B. ExchangeBiTree(T->rchild);
C. ExchangeBiTree(T->lchild->rchild);
